WEBVTT

1
00:00:25.625 --> 00:00:29.708
THE CAPITAL OF THE FIRE NATION

2
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:37.708
There he is!

3
00:00:38.291 --> 00:00:40.625
Stop the escape!
- Stop!

4
00:00:41.208 --> 00:00:42.250
Over there!

5
00:00:47.833 --> 00:00:49.166
Hurry up!

6
00:00:52.958 --> 00:00:54.291
Over there. grab it!

7
00:00:58.708 --> 00:01:01.166
Over there.
- Don't let him get away!

8
00:01:01.666 --> 00:01:02.750
Hurry up!

9
00:01:07.375 --> 00:01:08.291
After them!

10
00:01:13.041 --> 00:01:14.750
Stop!

11
00:01:33.166 --> 00:01:34.666
A surveyor.

12
00:01:37.458 --> 00:01:38.458
Hurry up!

13
00:02:02.958 --> 00:02:03.916
Come on!

14
00:02:04.666 --> 00:02:05.583
Let's go!

15
00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:08.625
After them!

16
00:02:13.208 --> 00:02:16.625
Take it to the King of Earth.
They're brewing a war!

17
00:02:16.625 --> 00:02:18.458
Over there!
- Leave now!

18
00:02:59.875 --> 00:03:01.083
You're too late.

19
00:03:01.083 --> 00:03:04.416
Your plans are already on the way
To the Kingdom of Earth.

20
00:03:04.416 --> 00:03:05.333
Good.

21
00:03:06.750 --> 00:03:09.583
That's where the eyes will be focused.

22
00:03:11.416 --> 00:03:13.083
Everyone except us.

23
00:03:16.250 --> 00:03:18.250
We are ready to attack.

24
00:03:18.958 --> 00:03:21.708
When your King gets the plans.

25
00:03:22.375 --> 00:03:29.250
he will lead his troops to your borders
and will rally other nations to his support.

26
00:03:29.250 --> 00:03:33.833
Water hyenas. wind shepherds
and the world -

27
00:03:33.833 --> 00:03:37.333
pay attention to the exporters.

28
00:03:43.583 --> 00:03:45.583
Did you want us to know?

29
00:03:49.208 --> 00:03:50.750
We are not your destination.

30
00:03:54.458 --> 00:03:56.666
Aim higher.

31
00:03:57.916 --> 00:04:00.833
Much higher.
- Why?

32
00:04:02.875 --> 00:04:03.958
Why are you doing this?

33
00:04:11.333 --> 00:04:13.750
Because our moment has come.

34
00:04:25.916 --> 00:04:28.333
Ingenious plot. nobility.

35
00:04:28.333 --> 00:04:31.958
Windbreakers are still not
a tactical threat.

36
00:04:33.083 --> 00:04:37.583
It's not about windbreakers.
It's about living among them.

37
00:04:37.583 --> 00:04:43.125
The only one who can defy us.
- The Avatar has not yet been revealed.

38
00:04:45.333 --> 00:04:48.291
That's why we kill them all.

39
00:04:56.666 --> 00:04:57.500
Water.

40
00:05:00.291 --> 00:05:01.250
Country.

41
00:05:03.958 --> 00:05:04.791
Fire.

42
00:05:07.625 --> 00:05:08.625
Aircraft.

43
00:05:12.291 --> 00:05:16.208
For millennia
four peoples have lived in harmony.

44
00:05:17.208 --> 00:05:19.791
That peace was brought about by the avatar.

45
00:05:23.583 --> 00:05:27.750
The only person.
who controls all four elements...

46
00:05:27.750 --> 00:05:30.833
and protects the fragile balance of nations.

47
00:05:35.125 --> 00:05:37.250
When one avatar dies.

48
00:05:37.250 --> 00:05:41.500
this soul is born into a new body
in an eternal cycle.

49
00:05:42.958 --> 00:05:48.666
A new manifestation has not yet appeared
since the previous avatar died.

50
00:05:48.666 --> 00:05:53.041
So I come to Lord Sozin.
the ruthless ruler of the fire nation.

51
00:05:53.041 --> 00:05:59.041
launches a relentless military campaign
to conquer the world.

52
00:05:59.041 --> 00:06:04.416
At first. Sozin decides to defeat the only one.
who might challenge him.

53
00:06:04.416 --> 00:06:07.000
The next ruler of the elements.

54
00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:13.333
A windbreaker that is not necessarily
not yet ready to become an avatar.

55
00:06:40.500 --> 00:06:46.250
SOUTHERN WIND TEMPLE

56
00:06:58.166 --> 00:06:59.208
Aang!

57
00:07:02.291 --> 00:07:03.166
Aang!

58
00:07:10.375 --> 00:07:11.666
Look!

59
00:07:18.958 --> 00:07:19.958
Is that Aang?

60
00:07:21.541 --> 00:07:22.666
Who else?

61
00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:39.083
The Spreader.

62
00:07:39.083 --> 00:07:41.458
Just admiring the scenery.

63
00:07:43.500 --> 00:07:47.500
The Tsutop monk is looking for you.
You skipped practice again!

64
00:07:47.500 --> 00:07:51.375
You know I already know how to
the same old workouts.

65
00:07:51.375 --> 00:07:52.375
Aang.

66
00:07:53.833 --> 00:07:58.416
You may be more advanced than others.
but you have a lot to learn.

67
00:07:59.083 --> 00:08:00.166
Believe it or not.

68
00:08:01.500 --> 00:08:06.250
one day you may hope
listened to your teachers more.

69
00:08:11.708 --> 00:08:16.750
You and other students need to help
in the preparations for the big comet festival.

70
00:08:17.750 --> 00:08:22.250
There is more work to do before
the other windsweepers arrive.

71
00:08:22.250 --> 00:08:23.583
How many are coming?

72
00:08:25.083 --> 00:08:26.500
What is that sound?

73
00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.166
Look over there!

74
00:08:30.375 --> 00:08:31.666
There are many.

75
00:08:34.083 --> 00:08:35.625
So many!

76
00:08:36.291 --> 00:08:38.958
Look at those!
- All of them.

77
00:08:41.541 --> 00:08:43.750
Come on. Aang! There they are!

78
00:08:45.208 --> 00:08:46.125
Wait!

79
00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:50.333
Did you tell him?

80
00:08:52.958 --> 00:08:55.166
The moment was not right.
- What?

81
00:08:55.750 --> 00:09:01.083
We cannot wait for the right moment.
We need to talk to the Council now.

82
00:09:08.375 --> 00:09:10.541
Aang has always been a child prodigy.

83
00:09:10.541 --> 00:09:15.583
The youngest fan in history.
who has earned the badge of a master.

84
00:09:16.166 --> 00:09:18.875
He is still only twelve.

85
00:09:18.875 --> 00:09:21.041
We cannot ask him to do this.

86
00:09:21.041 --> 00:09:23.541
Sozin attacks the Earth Kingdom.

87
00:09:23.541 --> 00:09:28.500
Water tribes send warriors.
and we too must help the exiles.

88
00:09:28.500 --> 00:09:30.125
We need an avatar.

89
00:09:30.125 --> 00:09:35.208
Aang is a powerful man.
but he still has a lot to learn.

90
00:09:35.208 --> 00:09:40.791
Responsibility. expectations. sacrifices.

91
00:09:41.875 --> 00:09:45.875
Above all. he needs to know.
who he is.

92
00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:53.416
If we send him inexperienced.
he may not meet our requirements.

93
00:09:54.958 --> 00:09:59.958
For that. he and the whole world
may never recover.

94
00:10:00.791 --> 00:10:06.458
The role of the avatar is a heavy responsibility.
not meant for a child.

95
00:10:06.458 --> 00:10:10.000
Our part is not
to choose who bears the burden.

96
00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:14.166
You've got too close to Aang
to see it. Brother Gyatso.

97
00:10:14.666 --> 00:10:18.333
Aang must leave immediately
to practice other spells.

98
00:10:18.916 --> 00:10:22.583
If only he still had time to help.

99
00:10:31.166 --> 00:10:33.250
Are all festivals hard work?

100
00:10:33.250 --> 00:10:38.833
The last one was held a hundred years ago.
and I wasn't alive then. if you can believe it.

101
00:10:39.666 --> 00:10:40.958
You wouldn't think so.

102
00:10:46.208 --> 00:10:50.416
Remember the last time I brought you here?
- That's when I got my tattoo.

103
00:10:50.416 --> 00:10:52.541
They are usually done in the main hall.

104
00:10:52.541 --> 00:10:56.958
I wanted you to have yours
in Yangchen's presence.

105
00:10:56.958 --> 00:10:59.791
The previous avatar of the wind shepherds.

106
00:10:59.791 --> 00:11:05.083
After his death. the following avatar was born
to another people in an eternal cycle.

107
00:11:05.083 --> 00:11:07.750
After Yangchen's death...

108
00:11:08.416 --> 00:11:13.125
came from the water sprites Kuruk.
The kingdom of Kyoshi...

109
00:11:13.125 --> 00:11:14.833
And the Roku of the fire nation.

110
00:11:14.833 --> 00:11:20.250
So the next avatar is
the windbender again.

111
00:11:20.875 --> 00:11:25.875
The spirit of Yangchen resonates in one of us.

112
00:11:27.166 --> 00:11:30.250
Aang. you have always been special.

113
00:11:30.916 --> 00:11:35.958
The most talented ventilator I know.
- I don't want to be special.

114
00:11:35.958 --> 00:11:37.041
You still are.

115
00:11:38.500 --> 00:11:43.458
Aang. you are the avatar.

116
00:11:46.958 --> 00:11:50.166
The fire has started down a dark road.

117
00:11:50.166 --> 00:11:53.208
It threatens to upset the balance of the world.

118
00:11:53.208 --> 00:11:59.708
Only the avatar. the master of the elements
can save the world.

119
00:12:00.708 --> 00:12:02.666
The world needs an avatar.

120
00:12:03.458 --> 00:12:05.708
The world needs you.

121
00:12:06.375 --> 00:12:09.875
You leave immediately
practice other spells.

122
00:12:10.833 --> 00:12:12.166
Just now?

123
00:12:12.166 --> 00:12:15.416
Would I abandon my friends. my home and you?

124
00:12:15.416 --> 00:12:19.583
This would be a huge burden for anyone.

125
00:12:21.166 --> 00:12:23.541
You're not just anyone.

126
00:12:23.541 --> 00:12:29.083
You are strong. kind and generous.

127
00:12:30.125 --> 00:12:34.000
Remember that. Always remember who you are.

128
00:12:34.666 --> 00:12:38.041
I can't think of anyone better.
to whom to bestow this power.

129
00:12:39.416 --> 00:12:42.541
I don't want that power.

130
00:12:43.250 --> 00:12:47.875
That's why you make a great avatar.

131
00:12:49.958 --> 00:12:52.083
Why do I have to be different?

132
00:12:53.125 --> 00:12:57.291
Can't I just keep pretending to be your friend?

133
00:13:00.333 --> 00:13:01.625
You are my friend.

134
00:13:03.208 --> 00:13:06.958
You will always be my friend.

135
00:13:45.291 --> 00:13:46.208
Moi. Appa.

136
00:13:48.416 --> 00:13:50.125
Can't you sleep either?

137
00:13:54.833 --> 00:13:57.625
Gyatso said that I am supposedly an avatar.

138
00:13:58.666 --> 00:13:59.583
Me.

139
00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:05.250
I'm not allowed to feed the bison calves either.
and I'm supposed to save the world?

140
00:14:07.916 --> 00:14:11.083
They say I have to remember who I am.

141
00:14:12.041 --> 00:14:13.916
I know who I am.

142
00:14:14.500 --> 00:14:19.000
I like windball. banana cake
and fooling around with friends.

143
00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:20.291
That's me.

144
00:14:21.083 --> 00:14:25.666
I can't stop
the fire nation or the war.

145
00:14:30.791 --> 00:14:36.541
For others. I'm lucky to have my talent.
but I'd change places at any time.

146
00:14:38.125 --> 00:14:41.916
I don't want to leave. I don't want the responsibility.

147
00:14:41.916 --> 00:14:44.916
I am afraid of power and of being alone!

148
00:14:55.250 --> 00:14:56.291
I'm scared.

149
00:15:06.083 --> 00:15:07.041
True.

150
00:15:07.625 --> 00:15:10.458
Flying always clears the mind.

151
00:15:12.208 --> 00:15:13.291
For now.

152
00:15:14.166 --> 00:15:15.166
Hop hop!

153
00:15:38.666 --> 00:15:42.041
Remember: no survivors.

154
00:16:05.708 --> 00:16:07.666
We're under attack!

155
00:16:48.750 --> 00:16:51.041
What is it now?
- Come with me!

156
00:16:52.583 --> 00:16:53.583
Where is Aang?

157
00:16:54.791 --> 00:16:57.541
Aang!

158
00:17:48.875 --> 00:17:50.375
I did.

159
00:17:58.125 --> 00:18:01.291
Rising storm. Shall we return home?

160
00:18:11.958 --> 00:18:16.208
Quickly. that's it!
Shut up. You'll be safe in the corner.

161
00:18:17.750 --> 00:18:19.041
Stay low.

162
00:18:56.458 --> 00:18:59.375
Don't worry. Appa! Hang in there!

163
00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:45.333
Another time you might have won.

164
00:20:49.791 --> 00:20:53.125
But not then.
when we have the power of the comet!

165
00:22:06.375 --> 00:22:10.291
SUSIVUONO

166
00:22:14.541 --> 00:22:15.541
Let's go!

167
00:22:19.208 --> 00:22:20.166
Thank you.

168
00:22:23.833 --> 00:22:25.083
All ears.

169
00:22:25.708 --> 00:22:32.500
The wall is watched in three-hour shifts.
but some of you can't seem to stay in position.

170
00:22:32.500 --> 00:22:33.791
From now on...

171
00:22:34.541 --> 00:22:37.916
two guards at once
that's twice as many shifts.

172
00:22:39.250 --> 00:22:42.916
Any complaints?
Me too. Keep working.

173
00:22:44.333 --> 00:22:45.625
Let's go.

174
00:22:46.166 --> 00:22:50.125
Where are we going?
- The fishermen returned without their catch.

175
00:22:50.125 --> 00:22:52.708
You always have to do everything yourself.

176
00:22:53.208 --> 00:22:57.250
They don't appreciate your leadership skills.
- They don't get it.

177
00:22:58.291 --> 00:22:59.500
Very funny.

178
00:23:02.750 --> 00:23:03.791
Katara!

179
00:23:11.125 --> 00:23:12.375
Where were you before?

180
00:23:15.125 --> 00:23:17.000
You made water spells again.

181
00:23:18.333 --> 00:23:22.333
Nobody saw me.
but it doesn't matter.

182
00:23:23.333 --> 00:23:26.208
If you are exposed
as a water trap for the fire nation...

183
00:23:26.208 --> 00:23:29.416
The fire has not approached the village for years.

184
00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:35.541
There's nothing to see in me either.
Even the sucker punching wine is more skilled than I am.

185
00:23:37.333 --> 00:23:38.666
It's for the best.

186
00:23:38.666 --> 00:23:44.458
You could help out more in the village.
- You don't always have to prepare for battle.

187
00:23:45.375 --> 00:23:48.416
We are at war.
- Water spells are our culture.

188
00:23:48.416 --> 00:23:50.666
Our job is to keep it alive.

189
00:23:50.666 --> 00:23:53.208
Our job is to survive.
- I know.

190
00:23:54.250 --> 00:23:57.166
If Dad were here...
- I am!

191
00:24:05.333 --> 00:24:06.166
Katara.

192
00:24:09.583 --> 00:24:12.291
Cheer later and paddle.

193
00:24:21.708 --> 00:24:24.166
Well done.
- I'm not doing this.

194
00:24:42.750 --> 00:24:44.125
Sokka!

195
00:24:51.916 --> 00:24:52.958
Does it hurt?

196
00:24:55.166 --> 00:24:57.833
Oh no. that's too bad.

197
00:25:03.166 --> 00:25:04.291
What is that?

198
00:25:09.125 --> 00:25:10.416
Strange.

199
00:25:18.625 --> 00:25:21.125
Let's grab a canoe. or we're fishin'.

200
00:25:22.791 --> 00:25:24.125
That would be ironic.

201
00:25:52.750 --> 00:25:54.625
Maybe I'll jump on an ice floe.

202
00:26:13.125 --> 00:26:14.000
Katara?

203
00:26:50.958 --> 00:26:51.916
Finally.

204
00:27:24.416 --> 00:27:27.458
Where did he come from?
- I don't know.

205
00:27:30.166 --> 00:27:32.083
Good. we're not dying.

206
00:27:33.583 --> 00:27:34.875
Let's go home.

207
00:27:37.916 --> 00:27:38.750
What are you doing?

208
00:27:39.333 --> 00:27:41.000
You're not going to leave him. are you?

209
00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:46.541
A glowing iceberg just exploded.
and a mysterious bald head popped out.

210
00:27:46.541 --> 00:27:50.083
Where did you get the idea to take her home?

211
00:27:50.083 --> 00:27:52.541
Sokka. he's just a child.

212
00:27:53.291 --> 00:27:55.666
We can't leave him here.

213
00:27:55.666 --> 00:28:00.916
Why should I be obeyed?
I am only responsible for the safety of the village.

214
00:28:18.916 --> 00:28:21.791
Looks like a carcass.
- What is that mark?

215
00:28:23.166 --> 00:28:24.375
I'm watching.

216
00:28:30.583 --> 00:28:32.000
It can't be.

217
00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:33.291
What is it. Grandma?

218
00:28:33.916 --> 00:28:36.500
This is a ventilator.

219
00:28:36.500 --> 00:28:40.000
Impossible. there are no more windbreakers.

220
00:28:40.666 --> 00:28:44.833
We won't get answers until he wakes up.
Let's let him rest.

221
00:28:46.458 --> 00:28:47.375
Come on.

222
00:28:58.583 --> 00:29:02.958
There is only a water tribe on the south bank.
That's where we have to go.

223
00:29:02.958 --> 00:29:05.583
Is that where the avatar is?
- That's right.

224
00:29:05.583 --> 00:29:06.791
Because of the light?

225
00:29:07.666 --> 00:29:09.125
Hourly?

226
00:29:10.916 --> 00:29:15.583
Sometimes the light rays are just
twinkling pieces of winter sky.

227
00:29:15.583 --> 00:29:19.583
For three years
I've been chasing every tip. every rumor...

228
00:29:19.583 --> 00:29:22.000
and whispers about the avatar.

229
00:29:22.625 --> 00:29:26.125
I will continue for another three years if necessary.

230
00:29:26.125 --> 00:29:29.000
Prince Zuko. I don't think your father wants...

231
00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:32.958
My father banished me until then.
until I find the avatar.

232
00:29:32.958 --> 00:29:35.125
That's exactly what I intend to do.

233
00:29:36.125 --> 00:29:43.125
It's just hard to watch your hopefulness
every time you see a sign.

234
00:29:48.666 --> 00:29:53.541
It will be worth all the effort. once I take
my place as heir to my lord of fire.

235
00:29:56.708 --> 00:30:00.708
Perhaps it is time to remember.
that the throne does not mean everything.

236
00:30:04.125 --> 00:30:05.500
Maybe not for you.

237
00:30:10.083 --> 00:30:11.166
For me again...

238
00:30:14.458 --> 00:30:15.791
It is my destiny.

239
00:30:40.958 --> 00:30:42.166
Come on!

240
00:30:53.500 --> 00:30:54.541
Come on!

241
00:31:07.666 --> 00:31:08.666
Hippa!

242
00:31:14.000 --> 00:31:14.916
Hippa!

243
00:31:15.500 --> 00:31:16.458
You're caught!

244
00:31:18.291 --> 00:31:20.875
Get out of there! What are you thinking?

245
00:31:20.875 --> 00:31:24.500
Have I not trained you
to stay alert?

246
00:31:24.500 --> 00:31:28.291
He can be the enemy.
- I am not an enemy.

247
00:31:28.875 --> 00:31:29.958
Who then?

248
00:31:30.916 --> 00:31:31.916
I'm Aang.

249
00:31:34.333 --> 00:31:35.333
Where am I?

250
00:31:35.916 --> 00:31:37.791
How did I end up here?
- You tell me.

251
00:31:37.791 --> 00:31:38.750
Wait a minute.

252
00:31:39.625 --> 00:31:40.458
Appa?

253
00:31:41.500 --> 00:31:44.041
Appa! Where is Appa?

254
00:31:45.750 --> 00:31:48.666
Sokka. have you seen that boy?

255
00:31:49.208 --> 00:31:50.125
I am.

256
00:31:50.958 --> 00:31:52.750
That's not strange at all.

257
00:31:54.541 --> 00:31:56.000
Appa!

258
00:31:56.000 --> 00:31:57.875
A wind-blower indeed.

259
00:32:08.791 --> 00:32:09.958
Have you seen Appa?

260
00:32:10.458 --> 00:32:12.000
Lentobiisoniani.

261
00:32:12.958 --> 00:32:16.875
Six legs. horns. brown arrowheads.

262
00:32:17.416 --> 00:32:18.666
Lentobison.

263
00:32:19.208 --> 00:32:22.041
Lentobison!
- It doesn't help to shout.

264
00:32:27.083 --> 00:32:28.333
What is that?

265
00:32:30.041 --> 00:32:31.333
Appa!

266
00:32:41.458 --> 00:32:42.458
Lentobison.

267
00:32:46.250 --> 00:32:49.166
So you were caught in a storm.
- It came up suddenly.

268
00:32:49.750 --> 00:32:54.041
The storm broke out after I left home.
from the southern windmill.

269
00:32:55.625 --> 00:33:00.083
That's where the wind scouts live.
or not all of them.

270
00:33:00.083 --> 00:33:03.041
The vast majority arrived
to the big comet festival.

271
00:33:03.041 --> 00:33:04.750
Comet Festival...

272
00:33:07.708 --> 00:33:08.875
Grandma?

273
00:33:11.166 --> 00:33:15.291
Water. earth. fire. air.

274
00:33:15.291 --> 00:33:19.333
A long time ago the four nations
lived in harmony.

275
00:33:19.333 --> 00:33:23.500
Then everything changed.
when the fire nation attacked.

276
00:33:24.083 --> 00:33:29.208
Only the avatar could prevent it.
the lord of the four elements.

277
00:33:30.041 --> 00:33:34.666
When the world needed him most.
he disappeared.

278
00:33:36.083 --> 00:33:42.125
So the fire sowed destruction.
We entered a dark age.

279
00:33:43.333 --> 00:33:45.875
The whole village knows this story.

280
00:33:46.750 --> 00:33:49.583
You wouldn't know. young man.

281
00:33:50.291 --> 00:33:56.125
You also don't know that windbreakers
have never been seen in living memory...

282
00:33:56.125 --> 00:33:59.708
and that the wind temple of the south
was the first to fall.

283
00:34:00.291 --> 00:34:03.875
because you were a prisoner of ice all this time.

284
00:34:03.875 --> 00:34:10.958
A large comet seen in the sky
last seen a hundred years ago.

285
00:34:17.708 --> 00:34:21.791
He may look like just a boy.
but he's more than that.

286
00:34:22.958 --> 00:34:26.083
He is the last fan.

287
00:34:34.625 --> 00:34:38.250
The prince dragged us
to the coldest corner of the world.

288
00:34:38.250 --> 00:34:41.458
Why the previous ones do not lead
to hot springs?

289
00:34:46.500 --> 00:34:48.916
You got a minute. Lieutenant Jee?
- No. sir.

290
00:34:50.958 --> 00:34:52.791
Let me clarify something.

291
00:34:52.791 --> 00:34:56.750
Our mission is vital
for the future of our people.

292
00:34:56.750 --> 00:34:59.041
So we're looking for an avatar.

293
00:34:59.750 --> 00:35:04.708
We show our value.
We will see our homes and families again.

294
00:35:08.041 --> 00:35:09.750
Or die trying.

295
00:35:23.541 --> 00:35:24.500
Are you OK?

296
00:35:27.041 --> 00:35:32.208
One hundred years. All my friends and acquaintances.

297
00:35:34.833 --> 00:35:36.083
Everyone is gone.

298
00:35:37.250 --> 00:35:38.625
I am sorry.

299
00:35:40.583 --> 00:35:43.458
I know how hard it is
it is to lose loved ones.

300
00:35:52.666 --> 00:35:55.833
When I was a kid. I didn't really understand this war.

301
00:35:56.541 --> 00:35:58.750
Then the firemen arrived.

302
00:36:00.833 --> 00:36:03.208
They destroyed everything in their path.

303
00:36:03.791 --> 00:36:04.750
Everything.

304
00:36:06.166 --> 00:36:07.083
Everyone.

305
00:36:10.416 --> 00:36:13.916
After that our father left
to hunt down the fire-eaters.

306
00:36:14.750 --> 00:36:18.000
We haven't seen him for three years.

307
00:36:19.500 --> 00:36:22.750
He left the reins to Soko
when he was only 13.

308
00:36:23.541 --> 00:36:25.000
I had to grow up fast.

309
00:36:26.833 --> 00:36:27.791
All of us.

310
00:36:30.625 --> 00:36:35.541
You are never really ready.
until you have to.

311
00:36:45.166 --> 00:36:48.541
They were the first attacks of the fire nation
against the water sprite.

312
00:36:49.291 --> 00:36:50.791
They were ruthless.

313
00:36:51.666 --> 00:36:55.166
Then the fire nation conquered
most of the world.

314
00:36:56.500 --> 00:37:00.416
Water farmers are still resisting
especially in the north.

315
00:37:00.416 --> 00:37:02.833
Earth's empire is still hanging on.

316
00:37:04.250 --> 00:37:05.250
I hope so.

317
00:37:08.500 --> 00:37:12.916
I had friends in the UK.
I used to visit them.

318
00:37:14.250 --> 00:37:18.833
No more visiting other nations.
Everyone stays with friends.

319
00:37:31.625 --> 00:37:37.333
Good. your skills are sharp.
- I'm about to meet the greatest of warriors.

320
00:37:37.833 --> 00:37:41.916
Avatar Kyoshi tamed
the exiles division with his own hands.

321
00:37:41.916 --> 00:37:47.375
You're ready for anything.
How about a cup of jasmine tea?

322
00:37:51.125 --> 00:37:54.666
Assume you can beat the avatar.

323
00:37:54.666 --> 00:37:58.416
That was a task your father thought impossible.

324
00:37:58.416 --> 00:38:03.916
That's why your homecoming might be
unexpected.

325
00:38:06.833 --> 00:38:08.208
You are mistaken.

326
00:38:18.625 --> 00:38:20.166
No one comes here.

327
00:38:21.500 --> 00:38:24.083
This place is quiet and hidden.

328
00:38:32.791 --> 00:38:34.291
You're a bouncer!

329
00:38:35.458 --> 00:38:40.708
Hardly. I'm trying to spar.
But I'm the only bender in the southern tribe.

330
00:38:40.708 --> 00:38:43.291
Sokka doesn't like my training.

331
00:38:43.291 --> 00:38:46.458
He fears the fire nation will get wind of it. and...

332
00:38:47.125 --> 00:38:48.166
And what?

333
00:38:49.625 --> 00:38:53.333
I'm the only waterer in the village for a reason.

334
00:38:54.166 --> 00:38:58.250
Everyone else was killed.
Sokka just doesn't get it.

335
00:38:59.375 --> 00:39:02.291
I am a warrior.
It is my duty to help our people.

336
00:39:04.541 --> 00:39:08.291
According to the monks. folding is about
energy and balance.

337
00:39:09.125 --> 00:39:13.250
Finding the balance
by feeling the energy around you.

338
00:39:13.250 --> 00:39:16.916
By finding balance. you can feel the energy.

339
00:39:46.208 --> 00:39:47.125
Good!

340
00:39:47.750 --> 00:39:49.500
I didn't even try.

341
00:39:49.500 --> 00:39:52.500
Good. I just need to let go.

342
00:39:58.416 --> 00:39:59.416
Katara?

343
00:40:08.958 --> 00:40:13.625
The fire is...
- We spotted them. Get into position!

344
00:40:15.625 --> 00:40:18.000
Throwers...
- Download them.

345
00:40:23.708 --> 00:40:29.416
Why did they come here?
What do they want after all this?

346
00:40:29.916 --> 00:40:31.083
Him.

347
00:40:31.958 --> 00:40:35.416
Aren't there more?
but the last ventilator?

348
00:40:36.833 --> 00:40:38.958
You are the avatar.

349
00:40:43.541 --> 00:40:44.375
Aang?

350
00:40:48.000 --> 00:40:49.500
I knew he was hiding something.

351
00:40:50.166 --> 00:40:54.000
When the world needed an avatar.
the coward disappeared.

352
00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:56.166
He escaped. and people died.

353
00:40:56.166 --> 00:40:58.333
They came ashore.

354
00:41:00.125 --> 00:41:01.083
Go into hiding.

355
00:41:01.083 --> 00:41:03.708
I want to...
- Right now.

356
00:41:06.958 --> 00:41:08.916
We need to get to safety.

357
00:41:26.458 --> 00:41:31.000
I am Prince Zuko.
I will become the firstborn son of Lord Ozai.

358
00:41:31.833 --> 00:41:34.000
We're not looking for your homes.

359
00:41:34.500 --> 00:41:37.666
We're just looking for someone who doesn't belong here.

360
00:41:38.375 --> 00:41:41.041
Someone who is not one of you.

361
00:41:42.250 --> 00:41:46.666
Hand him over immediately.
or I'll burn this place to the ground.

362
00:41:50.500 --> 00:41:53.083
Where is he?
- You must not give him up.

363
00:41:53.083 --> 00:41:55.375
He doesn't belong here.
- That would be wrong!

364
00:41:55.375 --> 00:41:59.791
My father told me to protect the village.
- But remember what Mum said.

365
00:42:00.541 --> 00:42:03.666
We need to protect them.
those who cannot.

366
00:42:03.666 --> 00:42:07.250
Aang has lost everything. He is an avatar!

367
00:42:07.250 --> 00:42:08.625
He lied about it!

368
00:42:09.625 --> 00:42:12.041
This has been a heavy responsibility for you.

369
00:42:13.041 --> 00:42:18.000
A manager does more than just fish.
Give others something to live for.

370
00:42:18.791 --> 00:42:21.000
That's what the avatar represents: hope.

371
00:42:21.916 --> 00:42:24.875
We need it as much as we need food.

372
00:42:25.875 --> 00:42:27.125
I know I do.

373
00:42:57.666 --> 00:43:00.916
I am Sokka. son of Hakoda.

374
00:43:00.916 --> 00:43:04.333
Well... the lord of snow and ice.

375
00:43:04.916 --> 00:43:10.125
In the name of the Susivuono water tribe
I demand that you leave immediately!

376
00:43:10.833 --> 00:43:14.583
If this is your chosen path.
so be it.

377
00:43:15.458 --> 00:43:19.333
Let's solve this between the two of us!
Do you need an army?

378
00:43:19.958 --> 00:43:22.333
I thought firebenders were tough.

379
00:43:22.333 --> 00:43:25.708
Don't go cheap.
We have a clear superiority.

380
00:43:25.708 --> 00:43:27.041
Dishonourable.

381
00:43:30.375 --> 00:43:31.416
I agree.

382
00:43:55.000 --> 00:43:56.583
Who needs an army?

383
00:44:09.041 --> 00:44:10.041
Leave him alone!

384
00:44:22.833 --> 00:44:23.708
Impossible.

385
00:44:50.875 --> 00:44:53.541
The game is over. Burn the whole place down.

386
00:44:54.791 --> 00:44:56.083
No!

387
00:44:56.625 --> 00:44:59.000
I surrender. as long as you leave them alone.

388
00:45:00.916 --> 00:45:02.541
It's me you're looking for.

389
00:45:05.791 --> 00:45:07.458
Grab it.
- Wait!

390
00:45:09.916 --> 00:45:11.083
No worries.

391
00:45:12.750 --> 00:45:14.625
I've never been defended before.

392
00:45:17.333 --> 00:45:19.958
You are the bravest person I have ever met.

393
00:45:53.000 --> 00:45:56.416
We have to help him somehow!

394
00:45:56.416 --> 00:46:00.625
Fix the gate supports
and don't slack off in training.

395
00:46:00.625 --> 00:46:03.250
They were watered down today.
- In training?

396
00:46:03.250 --> 00:46:08.375
Don't be intimidated by younger people.
You have to show them who's in charge.

397
00:46:09.833 --> 00:46:10.833
Take the lead.

398
00:46:12.041 --> 00:46:14.916
Let's save the weird kid.

399
00:46:27.208 --> 00:46:32.500
Many people other than me would not have believed
that this day would come.

400
00:46:33.583 --> 00:46:35.125
Can I ask you a question?

401
00:46:36.416 --> 00:46:37.458
Excuse me.

402
00:46:37.958 --> 00:46:40.958
I am Iroh. son of Azulon. Lord of the Fire.

403
00:46:42.166 --> 00:46:43.125
Just ask.

404
00:46:44.875 --> 00:46:47.208
Why did the fire nation start the war?

405
00:46:49.291 --> 00:46:55.166
According to some. our nature is
to expand and consume like fire.

406
00:46:56.208 --> 00:47:01.250
Others believe that stability will be achieved
only in our power.

407
00:47:01.833 --> 00:47:05.875
The aim of the conquests is to
peace and unity.

408
00:47:05.875 --> 00:47:10.208
Peace comes from respect for life
not killing.

409
00:47:10.208 --> 00:47:12.083
A noble cause. an avatar.

410
00:47:12.083 --> 00:47:17.500
After all. the majority view is that
the start of the war does not matter.

411
00:47:17.500 --> 00:47:19.583
The only difference is the end.

412
00:47:20.375 --> 00:47:26.375
It is believed that by imprisoning you
the people will finally do it.

413
00:47:27.541 --> 00:47:29.041
Do you believe the same?

414
00:47:32.125 --> 00:47:37.291
I have to go. but I'm looking forward to it
for our future conversations.

415
00:47:38.125 --> 00:47:41.958
In the meantime
I send you jasmine tea.

416
00:47:41.958 --> 00:47:43.416
It's reassuring.

417
00:48:15.041 --> 00:48:16.875
The hunt will be difficult.
- I know.

418
00:48:16.875 --> 00:48:20.166
Maybe we could follow
in their wake.

419
00:48:20.791 --> 00:48:21.958
Or...

420
00:48:23.125 --> 00:48:24.666
Let's go the other way.

421
00:48:26.333 --> 00:48:27.291
You're kidding.

422
00:48:28.250 --> 00:48:32.083
No way! There's no way you can get me
to get up from that...

423
00:49:03.208 --> 00:49:04.666
Avatars.

424
00:49:25.375 --> 00:49:26.791
Yes. sir!

425
00:49:45.125 --> 00:49:46.458
Stop!

426
00:49:47.666 --> 00:49:48.625
Grab it!

427
00:49:55.250 --> 00:49:56.958
Fire!

428
00:50:36.208 --> 00:50:37.041
Hello. sonny!

429
00:50:37.875 --> 00:50:39.000
Sokka!

430
00:51:36.625 --> 00:51:42.083
Thank you for coming to my rescue.
- We don't want flameheads jumping in our faces.

431
00:51:44.291 --> 00:51:48.375
Firefighters do not give up.
They will come after you.

432
00:51:48.375 --> 00:51:52.708
So we can't go home.
We would endanger others.

433
00:51:56.791 --> 00:51:57.958
Where to then?

434
00:53:23.416 --> 00:53:24.416
Gyatso.

435
00:53:33.625 --> 00:53:36.958
This would be a huge burden for anyone.

436
00:53:37.541 --> 00:53:39.625
You're not just anyone.

437
00:53:40.833 --> 00:53:46.083
You are strong. kind and generous.

438
00:53:47.083 --> 00:53:48.208
Remember that.

439
00:53:50.500 --> 00:53:52.833
Always remember who you are.

440
00:54:05.666 --> 00:54:06.708
Aang?

441
00:54:11.916 --> 00:54:14.500
What is he doing?

442
00:54:19.500 --> 00:54:21.333
Aang!
- Come on!

443
00:54:30.458 --> 00:54:31.291
Aang!

444
00:54:38.208 --> 00:54:40.500
Aang. stop!

445
00:54:44.375 --> 00:54:45.291
Please!

446
00:54:50.833 --> 00:54:51.875
Aang!

447
00:54:54.625 --> 00:54:55.541
Aang.

448
00:54:57.500 --> 00:55:03.500
I can't think of anyone better.
to whom to bestow this power.

449
00:55:07.666 --> 00:55:09.166
You are my friend.

450
00:55:11.041 --> 00:55:13.625
You will always be my friend.

451
00:56:16.833 --> 00:56:19.375
Don't get mad. but what was that?

452
00:56:20.125 --> 00:56:21.250
I don't know.

453
00:56:22.583 --> 00:56:24.291
This is new to me.

454
00:56:25.166 --> 00:56:27.958
The monks are gone. and I'm left alone.

455
00:56:29.333 --> 00:56:30.208
Listen.

456
00:56:31.416 --> 00:56:33.041
When you lose everything.

457
00:56:33.041 --> 00:56:38.041
then you realise how strong you are
and you learn to fight.

458
00:56:41.125 --> 00:56:44.416
They made a costly sacrifice for me.

459
00:56:45.000 --> 00:56:49.583
I'll make sure they didn't die in vain.
I have to do what they wanted me to do.

460
00:56:49.583 --> 00:56:54.541
I'll learn all the other spells
to restore balance to the world.

461
00:56:54.541 --> 00:56:55.708
Is that all?

462
00:56:56.833 --> 00:57:00.041
This was my home. and now it's gone.

463
00:57:03.208 --> 00:57:07.625
Only after we have lost something
we realise its importance.

464
00:57:12.583 --> 00:57:14.958
We will do whatever it takes to make it happen.

465
00:57:18.375 --> 00:57:19.333
Anything.

466
00:57:21.791 --> 00:57:25.708
I don't know where I'll end up
and whether this is where I want to be.

467
00:57:26.791 --> 00:57:28.458
I still know this.

468
00:57:30.291 --> 00:57:31.416
I am the avatar.

469
00:57:32.083 --> 00:57:34.333
This is just the beginning.

470
00:59:32.083 --> 00:59:35.000
Subtitles by Jouni Jussila
